org.vadere.state.scenario

Interface ScenarioElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AgentOSM, DynamicElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Agent, Car, Horse, HorseOSM, Obstacle, Pedestrian, PedestrianOSM, Source, Stairs, Target, TargetPedestrian, TargetQueue, Teleporter

    public interface ScenarioElement
extends java.lang.Cloneable
    The simulation scenario element is a brick in the simulation which may serve as a dynamic or static object. All scenario elements have a shape, which can be drawn in the simulation, an id which makes them addressable uniquely, a type which is yet limited to the types defined in ScenarioElementType and attributes.
